metadata.name: Battle Mage
metadata.description: MP will not regenerate naturally but Alucard can regain MP through use of a sword or the Mystic Pendant. Focuses on adding new spells and new enchantments to the game with new commands. The sword can be enchanted with ← → ↑ and Attack. More information on additional spells on SymphonyRando.FUN
author: MottZilla
eldri7ch
